Indegree : No of Pre-requisite tasks

start with 0 indegree tasks 
reduce -1 to it's parent when this task is done and do next 0 indegree task and go on until all are finished 

How do we find a cycle : Think there is a cycle then those nodes indegrees can never become 0 as they have a deadlock and we only go through nodes than we can traverse or indegrees become 0

what essentially we are doing is -> we are traversing what ever nodes we can 

